程序包 spark.jobserver.client

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    IJobServerClient
    Java client implements Rest APIs provided by Spark Job Server.
    IJobServerClientConstants
    Defines the constants used in public for the spark job server client.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    JarInfo
    Presents the information of spark job jar files, when calling GET /jars to a spark job server.
    JobConfig
    Presents the information of spark job configuration, when calling GET /jobs/<jobId>/config to a spark job server.
    JobInfo
    Presents the information of spark job result, when calling GET /jobs/<jobId> to a spark job server.
    JobInfo.Error  
    JobServerClient
    The default client implementation of IJobServerClient.
    JobServerClientFactory
    The factory is responsible for creating instance of IJobServerClient to communicate with the Job Server with the arranged rest apis.
    JobServerClientTest
    a test class for JobServerClientImpl
    Pojo  
  • 枚举概要 
    枚举 说明
    JobStatus  
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    JobServerClientException
    The exception indicates errors occurs when using instance of IJobServerClient.
